// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1056 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: faa9eb18-225e-5d2a-9812-6a1f149c8033

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*")
